=Episode 3=

00:00:13.344 --> 00:00:15.840
(Consort Wan, My Blade
Will Pierce You Sooner or Later)

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:21.280
That fool Sun Meizi!

00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:22.880
She wasted all my scheming.

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:25.240
Please calm your anger.

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:28.440
Madam Sun was insatiable and lustful.

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:30.840
Keeping her
would only bring disaster eventually.

00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:32.120
Fortunately,

00:00:32.120 --> 00:00:33.440
before she died, she kept silent

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:36.000
about secretly preparing
the medicinal guide for you.

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.560
She wouldn't dare reveal that.

00:00:40.120 --> 00:00:42.560
But with her dead,

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:45.080
we've lost the source of your medicine.

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:48.320
We'll need to find another way.

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:52.560
We can't let the supply
of Asuji Pills be cut off.

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:54.080
Yes.

00:00:54.080 --> 00:00:55.360
I will devise a solution.

00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:57.632
However,

00:00:57.880 --> 00:00:59.160
I heard

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:02.000
today Concubine Zhao and Wu Linfu

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:03.600
jointly punished Madam Sun.

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:07.400
Could they be conspiring
against Your Highness?

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:14.400
That dimwitted Zhao Lian'er
dares challenge me?

00:01:18.035 --> 00:01:20.320
(Fourteen Bureaus)

00:01:23.776 --> 00:01:24.840
Master,

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:26.680
Ling Yun from Fragrance Bureau
wants to see you.

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:28.240
I tried to send her away,

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:29.880
but she's kneeling outside.

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:32.000
She claims you knew she'd come tonight

00:01:32.280 --> 00:01:33.120
and expected her.

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:34.800
Let her in.

00:01:35.091 --> 00:01:36.115
Yes.

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.520
Chief Wu.

00:01:45.080 --> 00:01:46.000
What brings you here?

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:50.000
Though you burned the bridge
after crossing it,

00:01:50.520 --> 00:01:53.040
I won't break faith.

00:01:54.160 --> 00:01:56.720
I come to ask you

00:01:57.320 --> 00:01:58.960
if there are other tasks

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:00.720
you'd have me undertake.

00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:02.016
What?

00:02:02.160 --> 00:02:04.480
Do you wish to experience
all sixty-four torture methods

00:02:04.800 --> 00:02:06.160
of the Fourteen Bureaus?

00:02:06.528 --> 00:02:07.488
My lord,

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.880
you wouldn't repay kindness
with betrayal, right?

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:13.120
I helped you
secure the Fragrance Bureau.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:15.920
Now it fully obeys your command.

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:19.520
This strengthens your position
in the inner court.

00:02:19.880 --> 00:02:23.584
Isn't this merit worthy
of your trust in me?

00:02:23.584 --> 00:02:24.480
(The Imperial Kitchen's
Receipt and Clearance Ledger)

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:26.080
Cease your scheming.

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:27.960
You dare exploit me

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:31.240
for your own advancement?

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.840
You're only breathing now

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:36.760
because I showed mercy.

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:39.240
How dare you seek rewards?

00:02:41.480 --> 00:02:42.840
Without courage,

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:45.400
how could I serve under you, Chief Wu?

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:47.720
So you admit

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:49.600
you are using me?

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.960
To join your faction,

00:02:52.320 --> 00:02:54.120
I must first prove my worth.

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:57.520
Besides, using your influence
costs you nothing.

00:02:57.560 --> 00:02:59.640
The Fragrance Bureau
holds vital importance,

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:01.440
affecting all Six Palaces' safety.

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:04.600
The Head must be someone
I trust absolutely.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.200
Then

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:09.120
could I earn your trust?

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:28.800
What do you think?

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:34.848
Tong An.

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:50.960
I detest presumptuous people like you

00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:53.920
who dare scheme against me

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:56.240
and court death.

00:03:56.440 --> 00:03:59.040
Chief Wu, my loyalty is genuine.

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:00.760
Let me prove

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:02.680
I'm worthy of your trust.

00:04:03.160 --> 00:04:04.520
In the imperial harem,

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.960
only the words of the dead

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:08.680
are truly reliable.

00:04:21.880 --> 00:04:23.680
These are junks
cleared by Fourteen Bureaus.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.120
Send them away swiftly.

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:27.880
Today is Consort Wan's
coronation ceremony.

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:29.320
Be diligent in your duties.

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:30.400
Any negligence

00:04:30.840 --> 00:04:31.840
will be punished.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:33.824
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:39.240
Do you know what's in the box?

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:40.736
What?

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:42.880
A pretty young maid.

00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:45.680
Chief Wu is probably sending her

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:47.120
to his private residence

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:49.360
for his enjoyment.

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:57.560
Is there movement in the box?

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:00.440
Listen! Do you hear that?

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:17.160
Master, you should rest.

00:05:17.320 --> 00:05:18.360
I'll handle this.

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:20.240
Today is Consort Wan's
coronation ceremony.

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:21.472
Make no mistakes.

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:22.880
Understood.

00:05:26.280 --> 00:05:27.840
Go watch closely now.

00:05:28.467 --> 00:05:29.472
Yes.

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:43.760
How dare you show up again?

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:46.000
Do you truly not fear death?

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:48.960
My lord, you abused power
for a personal matter,

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:50.400
smuggling a palace maid out.

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.040
That's a capital offense.

00:05:52.640 --> 00:05:55.280
The Fourteen Bureaus
merely disciplined an impudent maid.

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:56.800
That won't cost my life.

00:05:57.480 --> 00:05:58.520
It's you who should worry.

00:05:58.547 --> 00:06:01.400
If you're here for the position
of Head of Fragrance Bureau,

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:04.000
I advise you to abandon your ambition.

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:06.720
My lord, you misunderstand.

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:09.080
My qualifications
are inferior to Shi Zhi's.

00:06:09.640 --> 00:06:11.400
I wholeheartedly accept your decision

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:13.000
of making her the Head.

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:14.816
However,

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:17.520
if you insist on expelling me
from the palace,

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:20.040
you'd effectively
be signing my death warrant.

00:06:22.640 --> 00:06:26.000
A scheming maid like you
won't survive long

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:28.040
in the palace anyway.

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:30.120
For your offense alone

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:33.480
of impersonating a eunuch
to infiltrate Fengxian Hall today,

00:06:33.640 --> 00:06:35.320
I could have you executed right now.

00:06:38.040 --> 00:06:39.920
If you dislike my eunuch attire,

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:40.992
- I'll remove it.
- You...

00:06:42.520 --> 00:06:45.200
Shameless! It's not a place
for your insolence.

00:06:47.296 --> 00:06:48.240
I...

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:49.840
I must remain in the palace.

00:06:50.640 --> 00:06:51.520
Let go of me!

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:52.360
I said no.

00:06:56.760 --> 00:06:57.960
Why do you insist on staying?

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:00.032
My lord,

00:07:00.640 --> 00:07:01.520
if I get expelled,

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:04.680
I'll be sold
to the Imperial Music Bureau.

00:07:06.440 --> 00:07:08.200
If you force me out,

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:10.720
you're delivering me to certain death.

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:15.872
Master,

00:07:16.080 --> 00:07:17.840
Consort Wan
is approaching Fengxian Hall.

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:20.288
Master?

00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:22.880
Return to the Fragrance Bureau.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.920
And cause no further trouble.

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:26.464
Otherwise,

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:27.560
even if I spare you now,

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.760
you'll not survive long.

00:07:35.840 --> 00:07:36.832
(Chief Wu,)

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:38.560
(the plan of using you)

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:40.160
(against Consort Wan won't do.)

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:42.880
(I'll have to betray you)

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:44.640
(and approach her myself.)

00:07:46.739 --> 00:07:49.376
(Fengxian Hall)

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:52.448
Shi Zhi.

00:07:52.840 --> 00:07:53.720
Ling Yun?

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:54.840
What are you doing here?

00:07:54.840 --> 00:07:56.560
Are you delivering the coronation gifts

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:58.240
for Consort Wan to Fengxian Hall?

00:07:58.336 --> 00:07:59.440
That's right.

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:00.320
I'm delivering

00:08:00.320 --> 00:08:02.200
our bureau's fragrance beads
for Her Highness.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:03.480
Shi Zhi,

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:06.000
might I request the honor
of presenting the beads

00:08:06.080 --> 00:08:06.920
to Her Highness?

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:09.360
You've newly arrived.

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:11.720
This task is too crucial for you.

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:15.600
Let me show you something.

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:33.480
The rest of you proceed.

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:34.464
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:08:37.040 --> 00:08:37.960
What do you want?

00:08:38.680 --> 00:08:39.680
By ancestral law,

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.560
each new emperor

00:08:41.640 --> 00:08:44.680
must appoint a proxy monk
to practice Buddhism in his stead.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:48.480
If I reveal your secret dealings
with the proxy monk,

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.560
what will happen?

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:52.032
What proxy monk?

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:53.120
I don't know him.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:54.144
Cease your slander!

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.296
Is that so?

00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:58.560
I found this jade pendant
among your belongings.

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:00.280
If you're unafraid,

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.680
I'll submit it
to the Disciplinary Court.

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:06.280
They'll thoroughly interrogate
your secret lover.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:07.584
Stop.

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:10.304
Shi Zhi,

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:12.360
if you grant me

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:14.160
the presentation duty
of the fragrance beads,

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:15.640
I will remain silent.

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:16.840
Not a word shall escape me.

00:09:25.640 --> 00:09:26.680
Where is the physician?

00:09:27.488 --> 00:09:28.544
Your Highness.

00:09:28.544 --> 00:09:29.440
Your Highness.

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:30.368
The physician arrives.

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:40.680
Physician Liu,

00:09:40.680 --> 00:09:42.800
why does Her Highness's cough persist?

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:44.160
Normally, the acupuncture

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.560
provides immediate relief.

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:47.040
Yet today,

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:48.000
this anomaly occurs.

00:09:49.160 --> 00:09:50.280
The auspicious hour is near.

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:51.200
What shall we do?

00:09:53.040 --> 00:09:54.080
Incompetent fools!

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:55.880
Please forgive me!

00:09:56.280 --> 00:09:57.160
Please calm down.

00:09:57.480 --> 00:09:58.800
You mustn't rage on this day.

00:09:58.920 --> 00:09:59.760
It's bad luck.

00:10:00.240 --> 00:10:01.152
Coughing like this,

00:10:01.280 --> 00:10:02.640
how shall I face His Majesty?

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.560
Do you wish my envious rivals

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:05.840
to witness my humiliation?

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:07.360
Please remain calm.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:10.280
Let Physician Liu
continue treating Your Highness.

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:14.200
Imperial Household Department,
Treasury, Workshops,

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:17.440
Fragrance Bureau, and others
present gifts to Your Highness.

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:19.600
May Your Highness's splendor
endure eternally

00:10:19.640 --> 00:10:21.360
and blessings flow abundantly.

00:10:23.520 --> 00:10:24.384
Your Highness,

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:26.680
(Shun Xi, Chief Eunuch)
a maid waiting outside claims

00:10:27.120 --> 00:10:29.360
she has a method
to stop Your Highness's coughing.

00:10:30.040 --> 00:10:31.080
What?

00:10:31.080 --> 00:10:33.480
How could a lowly maid
surpass imperial physicians in skill?

00:10:33.856 --> 00:10:34.960
Your Highness,

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:36.120
the hour can't be delayed.

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.320
How about

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:38.280
summoning her?

00:10:40.435 --> 00:10:41.280
Yes.

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:54.800
Ling Yun from the Fragrance Bureau

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:56.120
pays respects, Your Highness.

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:59.200
Did you claim
to cure my coughing ailment?

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:01.480
Yes, Your Highness.

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:07.480
The physicians couldn't help.

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:08.760
What method do you possess?

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:22.640
Your Highness need only
smell my medicinal fragrance

00:11:22.920 --> 00:11:23.960
to cease coughing.

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:50.200
What medicinal fragrance is this?

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:51.488
Your Highness,

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:54.840
it's a refreshing medicinal fragrance
made of blue mint and frost bamboo.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:58.880
Fresh blue mint is indeed excellent
for suppressing coughs,

00:11:59.240 --> 00:12:01.760
particularly effective
against pollen-induced coughing.

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:04.920
But this season doesn't yield blue mint.

00:12:06.160 --> 00:12:07.080
Indeed.

00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:09.520
I prepared the blue mint personally

00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:12.360
to stay alert during night shifts.

00:12:15.280 --> 00:12:16.256
Jin Yu,

00:12:16.840 --> 00:12:18.720
slap this wretch hard.

00:12:19.280 --> 00:12:20.160
Your Highness,

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:21.080
why punish me?

00:12:21.320 --> 00:12:22.600
My persistent coughing

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:24.360
baffles even imperial physicians.

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:26.560
Yet you alone possess the cure?

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:28.920
How could such convenience exist
in the world?

00:12:29.560 --> 00:12:30.400
I see

00:12:30.400 --> 00:12:31.920
this appears deliberate.

00:12:32.280 --> 00:12:34.320
You sought to shame me
on my coronation day.

00:12:34.752 --> 00:12:35.872
Slap her!

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:37.024
Hold!

00:12:38.040 --> 00:12:38.976
Your Highness,

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:41.600
please hear me out before punishing.

00:12:41.960 --> 00:12:43.920
I can not only cure your coughing,

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:45.280
but also know

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:47.120
who caused your ailment.

00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:51.488
Continue.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.200
Your coughing

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:55.280
was caused by the Fourteen Bureaus'

00:12:55.520 --> 00:12:56.680
Chief Wu Linfu.

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:01.080
Earlier,

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:02.640
I detected the scent

00:13:02.760 --> 00:13:04.320
of bitter orchid pollen on Chief Wu.

00:13:05.080 --> 00:13:07.400
Hearing of your condition today,

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:08.768
I realized

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:10.480
Chief Wu must have been near you.

00:13:11.320 --> 00:13:12.160
Bitter orchid pollen

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:14.840
easily triggers coughing
of sensitive people.

00:13:15.552 --> 00:13:16.480
I...

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:18.200
I must remain in the palace.

00:13:18.656 --> 00:13:19.520
No.

00:13:20.120 --> 00:13:21.152
Let me go!

00:13:28.320 --> 00:13:29.480
Bitter orchid's hot nature

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:32.320
causes respiratory distress
when sensitive people

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:33.960
inhale its pollen excessively.

00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:35.560
The entire palace knows

00:13:35.560 --> 00:13:37.880
Her Highness's allergy
to bitter orchid pollen.

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:39.320
Chief Wu,

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:40.400
your malice is boundless!

00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:42.080
Wu Linfu,

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:44.160
so it was you.

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:47.400
Despite your repeated insolence,

00:13:47.680 --> 00:13:49.120
I've shown forbearance.

00:13:49.560 --> 00:13:51.680
Now on my coronation day,

00:13:51.840 --> 00:13:53.200
you attempt harm through pollen.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:55.160
I shall inform His Majesty

00:13:55.520 --> 00:13:58.160
of your capital crime
against an imperial consort.

00:14:05.080 --> 00:14:05.952
Your Highness,

00:14:07.040 --> 00:14:09.400
I don't have bitter orchid pollen on me.

00:14:10.520 --> 00:14:12.440
Accusations require evidence.

00:14:14.840 --> 00:14:15.808
Wu Linfu!

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:18.720
Do you think us all blind?

00:14:19.160 --> 00:14:20.240
As an imperial consort,

00:14:20.640 --> 00:14:22.680
I'll not endure a servant's insolence!

00:14:22.920 --> 00:14:23.840
Your Highness,

00:14:24.040 --> 00:14:25.840
though I am a servant,

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:27.880
I serve His Majesty alone.

00:14:28.520 --> 00:14:30.080
I dare not overstep,

00:14:30.840 --> 00:14:31.800
but I am

00:14:32.200 --> 00:14:33.880
no sacrificial lamb.

00:14:37.640 --> 00:14:38.640
Very well.

00:14:39.920 --> 00:14:40.864
Wu Linfu,

00:14:41.640 --> 00:14:44.480
my patience with you ends now.

00:14:45.640 --> 00:14:47.040
We shall see who prevails.

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:49.184
Chief Wu,

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:50.920
Her Highness is merciful and kind.

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:52.880
Today is her big occasion.

00:14:53.240 --> 00:14:54.800
So she won't stoop to your level.

00:14:55.160 --> 00:14:56.520
But I must remind you,

00:14:57.160 --> 00:14:58.640
do not forget the palace rules.

00:14:59.160 --> 00:15:00.920
A servant who oversteps the station

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:02.600
will meet no good end.

00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:05.080
Well said.

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:08.360
You insolent maid
who oversteps the station.

00:15:09.840 --> 00:15:10.784
Guards!

00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:11.840
Your Highness,

00:15:12.080 --> 00:15:13.520
I treated you without permission

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:14.880
and boldly revealed the truth.

00:15:15.520 --> 00:15:17.200
All fault lies with me.

00:15:17.680 --> 00:15:18.656
Your Highness,

00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:20.800
I beg you to punish me.

00:15:24.520 --> 00:15:25.760
Come to me.

00:15:49.040 --> 00:15:51.000
I reward merit
and punish faults clearly.

00:15:51.920 --> 00:15:53.520
You contributed the most today.

00:15:54.360 --> 00:15:55.640
What reward do you seek?

00:15:56.840 --> 00:15:57.960
I desire no reward.

00:15:59.280 --> 00:16:00.840
My sole wish is to serve Your Highness.

00:16:07.480 --> 00:16:09.320
You wish to stay by my side?

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:12.560
What skills do you possess?

00:16:13.760 --> 00:16:15.480
I wish to be your blade.

00:16:16.840 --> 00:16:18.280
Whoever Your Highness targets,

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:20.160
even this dull blade of mine

00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:23.120
will pierce them till they shed blood.

00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:31.104
You may stay.

00:16:32.080 --> 00:16:32.920
From now on,

00:16:32.920 --> 00:16:34.440
you belong to Chengxi Palace.

00:16:35.520 --> 00:16:36.920
No one shall touch you.

00:16:41.920 --> 00:16:43.104
(Consort Wan,)

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:44.640
(my blade)

00:16:45.400 --> 00:16:47.240
(will pierce you sooner or later!)